BT /F2 13 Tf 54 652 Td (1. Project Overview) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 626 Td (Smart Attendance and Proxy Detection System is a MERN-style web application for managing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 612 Td (student attendance using short-lived QR codes and location verification. The system has) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598 Td (three main user roles:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 575 Td (- Student: scans attendance QR codes, views personal attendance, uploads assignments,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 561 Td (  downloads study material, and checks timetable.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 545 Td (- Teacher: generates live QR codes for a selected subject and section, monitors) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 531 Td (  attendance, exports reports, views defaulters, and uploads study material.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 515 Td (- Admin: monitors overall attendance statistics, QR validation history, section/subject) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 501 Td (  analytics, teacher/student counts, and defaulter summaries.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 478 Td (The main idea is to reduce proxy attendance by combining:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 455 Td (- Authenticated user identity through JWT.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 439 Td (- QR payloads signed using HMAC.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 423 Td (- Short QR expiry windows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 407 Td (- Teacher location captured during QR generation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 391 Td (- Student GPS location captured during scan.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 375 Td (- Radius-based distance validation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 359 Td (- Duplicate scan prevention per QR session and subject/day.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 343 Td (- Client device scan identifier checks.) Tj ET
54 320 m 541 320 l S
BT /F2 13 Tf 54 295 Td (2. Main Objectives) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 269 Td (- Digitize class attendance marking.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 253 Td (- Prevent students from marking attendance for absent classmates.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 237 Td (- Provide separate dashboards for students, teachers, and administrators.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 221 Td (- Generate subject-wise and monthly attendance reports.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 205 Td (- Identify students below required attendance thresholds.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 189 Td (- Maintain QR validation logs for administrative monitoring.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 173 Td (- Support study material and assignment document workflows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 157 Td (- Keep the application deployable on Render with MongoDB Atlas.) Tj ET
54 134 m 541 134 l S
