BT /F2 13 Tf 54 694 Td (9. Authentication and Authorization Flow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 668 Td (1. User selects a role on the login page: student, teacher, or admin.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 652 Td (2. Student logs in with roll number. Teacher/admin logs in with email.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 636 Td (3. Backend validates request with Joi.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 620 Td (4. Backend finds the matching user model based on role.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 604 Td (5. bcrypt compares the submitted password with the stored hash.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 588 Td (6. On success, backend signs a JWT containing user ID and role.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 572 Td (7. Frontend stores token and user object in local storage.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 556 Td (8. Frontend redirects user to the correct dashboard.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 540 Td (9. Protected APIs use `authenticate` middleware to verify JWT.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 524 Td (10. Role-specific APIs use `authorize\(...\)` middleware.) Tj ET
54 501 m 541 501 l S
BT /F2 13 Tf 54 476 Td (10. QR Attendance Flow) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 450 Td (Teacher Side) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 426 Td (1. Teacher logs in and opens the Teacher Dashboard.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 410 Td (2. Teacher selects section and subject.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 394 Td (3. Teacher clicks Generate QR Code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 378 Td (4. Browser asks for teacher location.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 362 Td (5. Frontend sends subject, section, latitude, longitude, and expiry seconds to backend.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 346 Td (6. Backend validates the request.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 330 Td (7. Backend deactivates old active sessions for the same teacher/subject/section.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 314 Td (8. Backend creates a new `QrSession`.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 298 Td (9. Backend creates a signed QR payload with session metadata.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 282 Td (10. Backend converts the signed payload to a QR image data URL.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 266 Td (11. Frontend displays the QR and starts a countdown timer.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 243 Td (Student Side) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 219 Td (1. Student logs in and opens the Student Dashboard.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 203 Td (2. Student clicks Open Scanner.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 187 Td (3. Browser requests camera access.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 171 Td (4. Student scans the teacher's live QR code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 155 Td (5. Frontend parses the QR JSON payload.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 139 Td (6. Browser requests student GPS location.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 123 Td (7. Frontend sends QR payload fields, student location, GPS accuracy, and client scan ID.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 62 107 Td (8. Backend verifies:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 91 Td (- JWT belongs to a student.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66 75 Td (- QR session exists.) Tj ET
54 42 m 541 42 l S
BT /F1 9 Tf 497 28 Td (Page 7) Tj ET
endstream
