BT /F2 13 Tf 54 510 Td (23. Viva and Interview Questions With Answers) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 484 Td (Project Basics) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 460 Td (Q1. What problem does this project solve?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444 Td (A. It digitizes attendance and reduces proxy attendance by requiring authenticated QR scans) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 430 Td (from students near the teacher's location.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 407 Td (Q2. Who are the users of the system?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 391 Td (A. Students, teachers, and admins.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 368 Td (Q3. What are the main modules?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 352 Td (A. Authentication, QR attendance, student dashboard, teacher dashboard, admin analytics,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 338 Td (timetable, document upload, and reports.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 315 Td (Q4. Why is it called a smart attendance system?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 299 Td (A. Because it uses QR codes, GPS validation, signed payloads, duplicate checks, analytics,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 285 Td (and automated warning flow instead of manual attendance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 262 Td (Q5. What makes it different from a normal attendance system?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 246 Td (A. A normal system may only record presence manually. This system verifies identity, time,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 232 Td (QR validity, section, GPS proximity, and duplicate scans.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 209 Td (Architecture) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 185 Td (Q6. Which architecture is used?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 169 Td (A. Client-server architecture with React frontend, Express backend, and MongoDB database.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 146 Td (Q7. Why did you separate frontend and backend?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 130 Td (A. Separation improves maintainability, allows independent deployment, and keeps UI logic) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 116 Td (separate from API/business logic.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 93 Td (Q8. What is the role of Express?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 77 Td (A. Express handles REST API routes, middleware, authentication checks, request validation,) Tj ET
54 42 m 541 42 l S
BT /F1 9 Tf 497 28 Td (Page 13) Tj ET
endstream
